    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_7_4614-4652",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4614-4652",
      "markText": "在将近一年的流放生活中，列宁坚持读书，开始钻研马克思主义理论。（07-11）",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4614&rangeEnd=4652",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4614&rangeEnd=4652"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_9_2191-2269",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2191-2269",
      "markText": "第一次提出了社会主义可能首先在少数甚至在单独一个资本主义国家内获得胜利的重要思想，丰富和发展了马克思主义，为俄国布尔什维克争取十月革命的胜利提供了理论指导。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2191&rangeEnd=2269",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2191&rangeEnd=2269"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_7_1681-1736",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1681-1736",
      "markText": "1898年娜·康·克鲁普斯卡娅也因在彼得堡从事革命活动被流放到这里。在流放地，列宁与克鲁普斯卡娅结成终身伴侣。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1681&rangeEnd=1736",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1681&rangeEnd=1736"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_6_3362-3386",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3362-3386",
      "markText": "她心地善良，为人正直，同情贫苦群众，富有正义感。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3362&rangeEnd=3386",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3362&rangeEnd=3386"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_6_10524-10593",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10524-10593",
      "markText": "他出色地完成了中学毕业考试，成为全班唯一荣获金质奖章的学生。他认真思考未来的人生道路，决心勇敢坚定地投身于斗争实践，去经受各种磨炼和考验。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10524&rangeEnd=10593",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10524&rangeEnd=10593"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_8_9584-9621",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "9584-9621",
      "markText": "“对社会主义意识形态的任何轻视和任何脱离，都意味着资产阶级意识形态的加强”",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9584&rangeEnd=9621",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9584&rangeEnd=9621"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_11_39091-39171",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "39091-39171",
      "markText": "“徒有其名的党员，就是白给，我们也不要。世界上只有我们这样的执政党，即革命工人阶级的党，才不追求党员数量的增加，而注意党员质量的提高和清洗‘混进党里来的人’。”",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=39091&rangeEnd=39171",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=39091&rangeEnd=39171"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_6_1655-1706",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1655-1706",
      "markText": "在中学高年级的时候，他第一次看到了在彼得堡上大学的哥哥亚历山大带回家的《资本论》，开始接触马克思主义。",
      "totalCount": 55,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1655&rangeEnd=1706",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1655&rangeEnd=1706"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_5_1561-1589",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1561-1589",
      "markText": "不只是开创了俄国历史的新纪元，而且开创了世界历史的新纪元",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1561&rangeEnd=1589",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1561&rangeEnd=1589"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_6_6068-6094",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6068-6094",
      "markText": "作为全班成绩最好的学生，列宁经常热心地帮助其他同学。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6068&rangeEnd=6094",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6068&rangeEnd=6094"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_8_2855-2891",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2855-2891",
      "markText": "1898年3月，俄国社会民主工党在明斯克召开的第一次代表大会上宣告成立。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2855&rangeEnd=2891",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2855&rangeEnd=2891"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33892203_8_13314-13355",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "13314-13355",
      "markText": "为什么它能够建立为无产阶级胜利所必需的铁的纪律并能在最困难的条件下坚持住这种纪律。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33892203&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=13314&rangeEnd=13355",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2cf324f07205276b2cfdbb5?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=13314&rangeEnd=13355"
    },
    {
